race.comment: REGAL WOLF (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 23.66 beating Tijuana Twinkle. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Great chance to get the job done again. LISSY'S GEM (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (23.87) from Box 3 at this track. Boasts a strong record from this draw with two wins and three minor placings from five starts. Expected to be in the finish again. UNSTABLE MABLE (7) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw then burst clear to score (23.77) at this track in Grade 4 over 407m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can measure up again. VELOCITY SMOLDER (6) placed last time out so worth considering.
